**Awwwards SOTD Mar 10, 2026 — ON Energy**

Glass UI 2.0 — not the blurry 2021 glassmorphism. Instead: near-zero fill + ultra-thin border + inset top highlight. The 1px inset white line is everything — it gives the panel physical thickness.

```css
.panel {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
}
```
